sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant KubeAuth as kube-auth-proxy
    participant NbCtrl as Notebook Controller (kubeflow)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API
    participant NbPod as Notebook Pod (JupyterLab)
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy
    participant PyPI as PyPI/Conda

    Note over User,PyPI: Workflow 4: Notebook Workbench Access

    User->>Dashboard: Login via kube-auth-proxy (OIDC/OAuth2)
    User->>Dashboard: Create Notebook from workbench image

    Dashboard->>K8s: Create Notebook CR (kubeflow.org/v1)
    NbCtrl->>NbCtrl: Reconcile Notebook CR
    NbCtrl->>K8s: Create StatefulSet, Service, HTTPRoute

    Note over NbPod: Pod starts with JupyterLab container, kube-rbac-proxy sidecar, PVC for user data

    User->>Dashboard: Click notebook URL
    Dashboard-->>User: Redirect to notebook path

    User->>KubeAuth: GET notebook path (via data-science-gateway)
    KubeAuth->>KubeAuth: Validate OIDC token
    KubeAuth->>KRBAC: Forward with identity headers
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBAC->>NbPod: Forward to JupyterLab (HTTP/8888)
    NbPod-->>User: JupyterLab UI

    User->>NbPod: Install packages
    NbPod->>PyPI: pip install (HTTPS/443)
    PyPI-->>NbPod: Package downloaded
